WEBVTT

00:04:59.083 --> 00:05:04.333
And Black women's bodies
are always already made genderless.

00:05:06.667 --> 00:05:07.958
End scene.

00:05:09.542 --> 00:05:12.309
From mammy and Sapphire,

00:05:12.333 --> 00:05:14.893
to Mandingo and Sambo,

00:05:14.917 --> 00:05:19.559
Black bodies and our genders
have been caught in the white imagination.

00:05:19.583 --> 00:05:22.518
And the imagination
of whiteness is fanciful,

00:05:22.542 --> 00:05:27.518
and powerful enough
to turn its fancies into realities.

00:05:27.542 --> 00:05:29.643
Imagined as a thing,

00:05:29.667 --> 00:05:32.268
we were made to become that thing,